Package: RUVcorr
Type: Package
Title: Removal of unwanted variation for gene-gene correlations and
    related analysis
Version: 1.4.2
Date: 2015-02-06
Author: Saskia Freytag
Maintainer: Saskia Freytag <freytag.s@wehi.edu.au>
Description: RUVcorr allows to apply global removal of unwanted variation
    (ridged version of RUV) to real and simulated gene expression data.
Imports:
